window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Audie Award, Paranormal, 2016 </b></p><p>Fifth in the fun, urban fantasy series that \"shines in a crowded genre\" (<i>USA Today</i>). </p><p>Angel finds herself in redneck hell when hordes of people descend on her hometown for the Deep South Zombie Fest - complete with zombie 5K runs, shamble-a-thons, costume contests, zombie paintball hayrides, and mock-zombie hunts. She intends to avoid the whole mess and focus on her upcoming college midterms - with the help of her stash of illicit zombie drugs - but that all changes when a decapitated body turns up at the edge of town.... </p>"; 
